{"tid":667686,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"影響 Windows 10 效能的防毒軟體排行榜報告 Windows Defender 竟然最嚴重","createTime":"2018-05-17T03:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T01:25:37.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"47073d0ce2b6e6bb88a118f5de48d12d9a819fe0","tid":667686,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:12:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/197108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kocpc.com.tw%2Farchives%2F197108&d=K5WjfG8rMEJ21Oddyi0VqJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=01148101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/197108</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然說很多防毒軟體公司都標榜安裝後不會影響 Windows 10 的效能，但實際是不是這樣，我想大家心裡都有數，為此，近期就有平台針對市面上 16 款防毒軟體進行測試，實際透過幾個日常使用情境，搭配上跑分軟體的分數，計算出一個影響分數的排行榜，沒想到落在最後一名的竟然是 Windows 10 內建的防毒軟體，可說跌破許多人的眼鏡啊！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://images.kocpc.com.tw/kocpc/2018/05/1526248296-24d10898149737fba3f219f6567838ea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.kocpc.com.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2018%2F05%2F1526248296-24d10898149737fba3f219f6567838ea.png&h=f025c95c&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0dbd41badddc1d50dea8250d9d8fcb7c6361c92d","tid":667686,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"近期國外專門進行系統測試研究的 AV-comparatives 獨立組織，就針對市面上 16 款防毒軟體，進行一輪佔用多少 Windows 10 系統效能的測試，其中幾款都是台灣讀者耳熟能詳的，如：Avast Free Antivirus、小紅傘（AVIRA Antivirus）、卡巴斯基（Kaspersky）、趨勢科技（Trend Micro）、以及微軟內建的 Windows Defender 等等，下方是完整名單，後面數字代表軟體版本：<br />\n<br />\n1. Avast Free Antivirus 18.3<br />\n2. AVG Free Antivirus 18.3<br />\n3. AVIRA Antivirus Pro 15.0<br />\n4. Bitdefender Internet Security 22.0<br />\n5. BullGuard Internet Security 18.0<br />\n6. Emsisoft Anti-Malware 2018.3<br />\n7. ESET Internet Security 11.1<br />\n8. F-Secure SAFE 17.204<br />\n9. K7 Total Security 15.1<br />\n10. Kaspersky Internet Security 18.0<br />\n11. McAfee Internet Security 21.1<br />\n12. Microsoft Windows Defender 4.14<br />\n13. Panda Free Antivirus 18.5<br />\n14. Quick Heal Total Security 17.0<br />\n15. Symantec Norton Security 22.14<br />\n16. Tencent PC Manager 12.3 (English)<br />\n17. Trend Micro Internet Security 12.0<br />\n19. VIPRE Advanced Security 10.1<br />\n<br />\n首先先進行六大項日常使用的測試，包括：複製檔案（File copying）、壓縮與解壓縮（Archiving and unarchiving）、安裝與解除安裝應用程式（Installing/uninstalling applications）、啟動應用程式（Launching applications）、下載檔案（Downloading files）以及網頁瀏覽（Browsing Websites）。<br />\n<br />\n下方就是結果，綠色長條越多代表速度越快，在測試下拿到滿分的只有一位 「K7 Total Security」，卡巴斯基與 Bitdefender 表現也不錯，落在後面兩位的則是 Quick Heal 與 Microsoft Windows Defender，其中 Windows 內建的 Windows Defender 竟然拖垮複製檔案、壓縮與解壓縮不少，出乎意料之外，照道理說相容性應該最好才對：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://images.kocpc.com.tw/kocpc/2018/05/1526248278-cd22668800fe3013a450e5f6a9042c91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.kocpc.com.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2018%2F05%2F1526248278-cd22668800fe3013a450e5f6a9042c91.png&h=9bbb9b77&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"781511c6c9712107bf320c8faedb0efb44b10941","tid":667686,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:15:41.000Z","msg":"再來他們也加入 PC MARK 的跑分測試，Baseline 為未安裝任何防毒軟體的情況下，小紅傘、F-Secure、ESET 都拿下非常高的分數：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://images.kocpc.com.tw/kocpc/2018/05/1526248285-97a714d11958e2924a65628f0ea811d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.kocpc.com.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2018%2F05%2F1526248285-97a714d11958e2924a65628f0ea811d4.png&h=6cd63513&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n接下來把這兩項分數相加起來，給予一個影響分數，K7 獲得最第一名，只有少少的 2 分影響程度，其次是 ESET、Avast、Bitdefender 等，雖然 Microsoft Windows Defender 在 PC MARK 跑分上贏過 Quick Heal 一些，但日常使用測試下影響太多，因此總分相加還是落在最後一名，影響分數高達 33.3 分，真的是有點高：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://images.kocpc.com.tw/kocpc/2018/05/1526248290-e3b8a99ee405020cdff966fc1b6b57e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.kocpc.com.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2018%2F05%2F1526248290-e3b8a99ee405020cdff966fc1b6b57e0.png&h=fda68e1a&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a339e3a37be6749640e98ed2ddf5a117884b9bb0","tid":667686,"uid":38820,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:15:44.000Z","msg":"in Bitdefender, I TRUST!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fd483f5ef5a06af58c9799ac011e980592e1d9","tid":667686,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:16:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">ADVANCE+ 為他們最推薦的幾套防毒軟體，越下方越不推薦：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.kocpc.com.tw/kocpc/2018/05/1526248303-29bfca767ebeca677d1966caf66bcaad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.kocpc.com.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2018%2F05%2F1526248303-29bfca767ebeca677d1966caf66bcaad.png&h=4b89d5de&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d923f1db1361b7dca6f8e920dfc22d75208d5493","tid":667686,"uid":87433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"360安全衛士世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8fee1e1778c3b636a759ecf8a518ac5e8f04ac","tid":667686,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c462abbda8aefd3b5bac4e6238d952607146857c","tid":667686,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aa8fee1e1778c3b636a759ecf8a518ac5e8f04ac","tid":667686,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:20:45.000Z","msg":"要打機，不了"},{"pid":"dc42e233f028773538c27b74d5a4ec39d3c2cf88","tid":667686,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:20:50.000Z","msg":"Tencent <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /